data.title: protein interaction and molecular dynamics analysis for identification of novel inhibitors in Burkholderia cepacia GG4
data.meta_description: The lack of complete treatments and appearance of multiple drug-resistance strains of Burkholderia cepacia complex (Bcc) are causing an increased risk of lung infections in cystic fibrosis patients.
